{
  "name": "upload_card",
  "dsl": {
    "schema": "2.0",
    "header": {
      "title": { "tag": "plain_text", "content": "数据上传阶段" },
      "template": "green"
    },
    "body": {
      "elements": [
        {
          "tag": "markdown",
          "content": "**数据上传阶段提醒**：请根据卡片提示完成数据上传与自检。"
        },
        {
          "tag": "column_set",
          "columns": [
            {
              "tag": "column",
              "elements": [
                { "tag": "markdown", "content": "**需求编号：** {{需求编号}}" },
                { "tag": "markdown", "content": "**标题：** {{标题}}" },
                { "tag": "markdown", "content": "**数据批次号：** {{数据批次号}}" }
              ]
            },
            {
              "tag": "column",
              "elements": [
                { "tag": "markdown", "content": "**上传人：** {{上传人}}" },
                { "tag": "markdown", "content": "**数据来源：** {{数据来源}}" },
                { "tag": "markdown", "content": "**样本量：** {{样本量}}" }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tag": "markdown",
          "content": "在多维表中查看待处理批次并更新校验结果。"
        },
        {
          "tag": "button",
          "text": { "tag": "plain_text", "content": "打开待校验视图" },
          "type": "primary",
          "behaviors": [
            {
              "type": "open_url",
              "default_url": "https://bytedance.larkoffice.com/base/DQE2bkPVba3cI5sh30ocyGh8ngh?table=tblTytNnabjCkezy&view=vewRtrWchK"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  }
}
